snippet.title: "Ed-0: Zombie Uprising" Gameplay Guidance Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to "Ed-0: Zombie Uprising¸" a new rogue-like action survival title.
Early access on Steam is now available!
The "Gameplay Guidance Trailer" explains how to experience the excitement of this title!

◆Gameplay Guidance Trailer
The trailer will explain in detail how to enjoy "rogue-like" and "battles," 
and is a must-see for those who are willing to play the game!

▼Purchase from here (Steam Store)
https://store.steampowered.com/agecheck/app/1717020/

▼Feedbacks from here (Official Discord)
https://discord.gg/4dMMPXqKV3

▼"Ed-0: Zombie Uprising" Official Website
https://www.d3p.co.jp/ed-0/

▼D3P Official Twitter
https://twitter.com/D3_PUBLISHER
